parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx^.Here he is. Just like you asked.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlOp.What would I do without you, Nellie?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlOp.Not many people have gotten under my skin like you have.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.She’s not the type to tell fibs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaDe.I was a thief when I met your mother… Not many people knew that though.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.So… This is the life you chose to live?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.Had I known your mother was pregnant, I might have stuck around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.I’ve spent a long time looking for you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe.Andrea’s been playing you like a fiddle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.She’s my boss. Isn’t that how it works?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaOp.If you’re the type to get played… Sure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.I’m not the only one taking orders from her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlOp.Stick around long enough and maybe you’ll end up with one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.You’ve made my life difficult… But it sounds like I’m going to be your best friend.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.All the glory is coming your way. I’m going to feed you till you're full and fat.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.So you know what Andrea’s plan is?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.It’s not the worst idea… At least I get to keep what I’ve built.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.It’s not my choice. I’d have you locked up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.Hey, I wasn’t like me either… You’re young.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.Vayne is not going to get between us… If we’re in this together, you and me… we have to talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.I’m planning to be a good boy, and I hope you do the same.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.I’ve played along so far, haven’t I?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.She wanted to have my men killed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.Heh… Still… She’s not going to pull her punches just because I’m the big, scary bad guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.And you want the heads up if she decides to throw you away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.If I can’t trust my own flesh and blood, then who can I trust?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.Vayne doesn’t want you here. So you better keep a low profile... ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnDe.I trust my men, but that woman has a way of getting what she wants.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.I see that twinkle in your eye, 1Hero. You and me… We’re the same.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Duncan is looking for allies if things go south. I'm in the perfect situation for him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.Good for you. It means you can stay close.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Yeah… I suppose that’s one way to look at it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.It wasn’t easy, but Lillian had them locked away in magic chests.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Keep an eye on the rift, but be careful…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I assume that Lillian doesn’t have an internet connection in Hell, so she’ll be bringing the Toma here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx.If I see any monsters, I’m shooting them immediately.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Try what you can, but the most important thing you need to remember is to never look at the Toma…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.If you see someone holding a statue, don’t look at it…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Come on, 1Hero. Let’s see what the priest suggests we do next.");
